### Test Graph API to check if columns are included

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7189
@connectionId = c1034bfe-ede7-4291-8ba2-0feef5c75fd5
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Get Graph Data
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/graph
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Clear Cache (if needed)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/cache
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Re-analyze Database
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/analyze?forceRefresh=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Get Graph Data Again (should have columns now)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/graph
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
